author: Audrey McNamara
title: Crowds gather at North Carolina Capitol to protest stay-at-home order
description: People once again gathered in Raleigh North Carolina on Tuesday to protest thee governor's stay-at-home order.
content: People in North Carolina have gathered around the state's Capitol in Raleigh to protest Governor Roy Cooper's stay-at-home order. Protesters, disobeying social distancing guidelines, marched around the governor's mansion holding signs that read "let us work,"… [+3220 chars]
